  "text": "We incorporated prior sentiment information into the model using sentiment seed words in analogy to [CITATION_1] . After running the sampler for a burnin period of 500 iterations, we interleaved it with the optimizer, optimizing over y ki and y ji every 100 th step of sampling. We trained the model in 2000 iterations for both data sets and used the last sample in the chain in all of our experiments.",
